r, November, December"}},"buy_buttons":{"type":"buy_buttons","settings":{"show_dynamic_checkout":false,"skip_cart":false,"uppercase_text":false}},"98db29ee-a7dc-429e-8129-bf71131627da":{"type":"payment_badges","settings":{"enabled_payment_types":""}},"de244682-4323-4802-b4ba-b79b08e0c71d":{"type":"emoji_benefits","disabled":true,"settings":{"benefits":"<p><\/p><p><strong>GRATIS VERZENDING VANAF €20<br\/><br\/>30 DAGEN BEDENKTIJD<\/strong><\/p>"}},"d505cdfe-d5cf-4aff-8e9e-abca6dae66eb":{"type":"sticky_atc","settings":{"display_when":"always","button_label":"In den Warenkorb legen","color_scheme":"background-1"}},"149aabfb-9fd8-4472-a633-6032dbe01ed0":{"type":"reviews","disabled":true,"settings":{"avatar_alignment":"top","author_1":"Kyle","text_1":"<p>\"Een mooie toevoeging bij mijn huis, ze zijn heel handig voor in de slaapkamer!\"<\/p>","author_2":"Lisa","text_2":"<p>\"Hele leuke lampen! Ik heb er 2 in de slaapkamer en 1 in de woonkamer, super handig.\"<\/p>","author_3":"","text_3":""}},"icon_with_text_H3PrfA":{"type":"icon_with_text","settings":{"layout":"vertical","icon_1":"truck","heading_1":"Kostenloser Versand ab 20€","icon_2":"return","heading_2":"30 Tage Rückgabegarantie","icon_3":"price_tag","image_3":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/image-removebg-preview.png","heading_3":"Bezahlen Sie später mit Klarna"}}},"block_order":["e9c7700d-8020-4263-9b68-bdde2669877b","title","price","44f9cdc2-f4bf-466e-87d5-fb765ad4864a","48b7eaf2-2c4d-4d42-a430-ab9107e675d0","198d0806-84ef-471c-a05b-86232a4c0083","2edbf491-d07c-4718-b71e-18ffe22ab7dc","buy_buttons","98db29ee-a7dc-429e-8129-bf71131627da","de244682-4323-4802-b4ba-b79b08e0c71d","d505cdfe-d5cf-4aff-8e9e-abca6dae66eb","149aabfb-9fd8-4472-a633-6032dbe01ed0","icon_with_text_H3PrfA"],"custom_css":[],"settings":{"enable_sticky_info":true,"hide_variants":false,"image_zoom":"none","dots_color_scheme":"inverse","enable_video_looping":false,"media_size":"medium","media_position":"left","gallery_layout":"thumbnail_slider","constrain_to_viewport":true,"media_fit":"contain","mobile_media_corner_radius":0,"mobile_pagination":"dots_overlay","trust_badge":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/1_1_GRATIS_Luminate_logo.png","trust_badge_position":"top-right","trust_badge_size":"large"}},"fb5ad6ac-1898-431f-b29d-f6d26831fba9":{"type":"collapsible-content","blocks":{"template--20404861862212__fb5ad6ac-1898-431f-b29d-f6d26831fba9-collapsible_row-1":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Spezifikationen","icon":"none","row_content":"<p><strong>Dimmbar:<\/strong> Ja, in drei Stufen<\/p><p><strong>Stromquelle:<\/strong> LED<\/p><p><strong>Maximale Leistung:<\/strong> 5W<\/p><p><strong>Wiederaufladbar:<\/strong> USB-C (im Lieferumfang enthalten)<\/p><p><strong>Größe:<\/strong> 21 cm (Höhe) x 9 cm (Breite)<\/p>","page":""}},"template--20404861862212__fb5ad6ac-1898-431f-b29d-f6d26831fba9-collapsible_row-2":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Bedienungsanleitung","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Schalten Sie die Lampe mit dem Knopf an der Unterseite ein. Dimmen Sie die Lampe mit der Touch-Bedienung oben. Halten Sie die Touch-Bedienung gedrückt, um zwischen warmem, neutralem und weißem Licht zu wechseln.<\/p>","page":""}},"template--20404861862212__fb5ad6ac-1898-431f-b29d-f6d26831fba9-collapsible_row-3":{"type":"collapsible_row","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"Opladen","icon":"lightning_bolt","row_content":"<p>Laad eenvoudig op via de meegeleverde USB-C-kabel voor ruim 48 uur ononderbroken verlichting. Bij de Karakter Lamp staat niet alleen het voortreffelijke ontwerp centraal, maar ook jouw veiligheid. Onze lampen worden aangedreven door een beveiligde batterij met geavanceerde overstroomtechnologie, wat voldoet aan explosieveilige en vlambestendige veiligheidsnormen<\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["template--20404861862212__fb5ad6ac-1898-431f-b29d-f6d26831fba9-collapsible_row-1","template--20404861862212__fb5ad6ac-1898-431f-b29d-f6d26831fba9-collapsible_row-2","template--20404861862212__fb5ad6ac-1898-431f-b29d-f6d26831fba9-collapsible_row-3"],"settings":{"caption":"","heading_size":"h1","heading_alignment":"center","layout":"none","color_scheme":"background-1","container_color_scheme":"background-2","open_first_collapsible_row":false,"image_ratio":"adapt","desktop_layout":"image_second","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":8}},"testimonials_cfdjrq":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"column_jq9wpf":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"","text":"<p><em>Perfekt für mein Geschäft! Die Lampe hat eine lange Lebensdauer und schafft eine großartige Atmosphäre, die meine Kunden wirklich zu schätzen wissen.<\/em><\/p>","author":"Danny H."}},"column_KGQXyb":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"","text":"<p><em>Diese Lampe ist eine stilvolle Ergänzung für mein Wohnzimmer. Die Touch-Bedienung funktioniert reibungslos, und ich finde es großartig, dass ich zwischen warmem und hellem Licht wechseln kann.<\/em><\/p>","author":"Maria S."}},"column_YafX7J":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"","text":"<p><em>Sehr zufrieden mit meinem Kauf. Die Lampe ist einfach zu bedienen und passt perfekt zu meinem modernen Interieur. Absolut empfehlenswert!<\/em><\/p>","author":"Sander V."}}},"block_order":["column_jq9wpf","column_KGQXyb","column_YafX7J"],"settings":{"title":"Was unsere Kunden sagen","heading_size":"h1","text":"","color_scheme":"background-1","image_width":"full","image_ratio":"square","column_alignment":"center","show_stars":true,"show_quotes":true,"columns_desktop":3,"padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"3d07fd2e-22b5-4988-88fb-ca0b0e7cb741":{"type":"collapsible-content","blocks":{"template--20404861862212__3d07fd2e-22b5-4988-88fb-ca0b0e7cb741-collapsible_row-1":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Product specificaties","icon":"none","row_content":"<p><strong>Dimbaar:<\/strong>Ja, in drie stappen<br\/><strong>Certificaat: <\/strong>CE<br\/><strong>Stroombron: <\/strong>LED<br\/><strong>Maximaal vermogen:<\/strong>5W<br\/><strong>Spanning:<\/strong>5V<br\/><strong>Grootte: <\/strong>21cm (hoogte) x 9cm (breedte)<\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["template--20404861862212__3d07fd2e-22b5-4988-88fb-ca0b0e7cb741-collapsible_row-1"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"caption":"","heading_size":"h1","heading_alignment":"center","layout":"none","color_scheme":"background-1","container_color_scheme":"background-2","open_first_collapsible_row":false,"image_ratio":"adapt","desktop_layout":"image_second","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":4}},"related-products":{"type":"related-products","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading_size":"h2","products_to_show":4,"columns_desktop":4,"color_scheme":"background-1","image_ratio":"adapt","show_secondary_image":false,"show_vendor":false,"show_rating":false,"columns_mobile":"2","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":24}},"7c2381c3-1795-445b-91da-9765523b1638":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"caption_BRUVwh":{"type":"caption","settings":{"caption":"ALLROUND","text_style":"caption-with-letter-spacing","text_size":"medium"}},"heading_eQajNd":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading_size":"h1"}},"template--19900162113860__7c2381c3-1795-445b-91da-9765523b1638-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Ob Sie Ihr Zuhause verschönern oder eine gemütliche Atmosphäre in Ihrem <strong>Restaurant oder Ihrer Bar <\/strong>schaffen möchten – diese Lampe ist ein vielseitiges Accessoire. Verwenden Sie sie als Tischlampe, Nachttischlampe oder stimmungsvolle Ergänzung in jedem Raum.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["caption_BRUVwh","heading_eQajNd","template--19900162113860__7c2381c3-1795-445b-91da-9765523b1638-text-1"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/4_9adeac45-0018-433a-9a36-6521577d3986.webp","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"7ead9d52-a3ce-4f63-9e00-e5fbe252c5a8":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"caption_MeYD8U":{"type":"caption","settings":{"caption":"WHY LUMINATE?","text_style":"caption-with-letter-spacing","text_size":"medium"}},"heading_JLkj7e":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading_size":"h2"}},"9bd8fb44-fa40-449d-be77-8f37af118496":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><strong>Stimmungsvolles Licht:<\/strong> Schafft eine warme und gemütliche Atmosphäre.<br\/><strong>Warmes & Weißes Licht:<\/strong> Wählen Sie einfach zwischen warmem und weißem Licht für die perfekte Stimmung in jedem Raum.<br\/><strong>Dimmbar:<\/strong> Passen Sie das Licht mit der Touch-Bedienung in 3 Stufen an – von sanft bis hell.<br\/><strong>Langlebiges Material:<\/strong> Hergestellt aus hochwertigem Metall für eine lange Lebensdauer.<br\/><strong>Kabellos:<\/strong> Genießen Sie Flexibilität und Komfort, ganz ohne Kabel.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["caption_MeYD8U","heading_JLkj7e","9bd8fb44-fa40-449d-be77-8f37af118496"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/gif_2_50424d90-f982-49f3-9978-e3fd7ae6da8e.webp","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"text_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"2cb68c65-93ce-4030-a625-5bac24b42fe4":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"caption_W9Mt9x":{"type":"caption","settings":{"caption":"SUSTAINABILITY","text_style":"caption-with-letter-spacing","text_size":"medium"}},"heading_gGLCbq":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading_size":"h1"}},"f1d0c312-6e0a-443f-a521-b731697ad34f":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Die Luminate Tischlampe verwendet energieeffiziente LED-Leuchten, die dir helfen, <strong>Energiekosten zu sparen<\/strong> und gleichzeitig einen Beitrag zum Umweltschutz zu leisten.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["caption_W9Mt9x","heading_gGLCbq","f1d0c312-6e0a-443f-a521-b731697ad34f"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/5_cfabdbfe-307a-42d2-b90f-6aac655326a5.webp","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"9f8ed1f4-75b8-4974-842c-754126d14d2b":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"caption_CxKtjU":{"type":"caption","settings":{"caption":"DESIGN","text_style":"subtitle","text_size":"medium"}},"heading_HzfMpD":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading_size":"h1"}},"17763526-3cb0-4bec-9275-ca6d59d9a612":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Die luxuriöse Luminate Tischlampe zeichnet sich durch ein elegantes und auffälliges Design aus. Ihre klare Silhouette und die hochwertigen Materialien machen sie zu einer perfekten Ergänzung für jedes <strong>Zuhause, Hotel oder Restaurant.<\/strong><\/p>","text_style":"body"}}},"block_order":["caption_CxKtjU","heading_HzfMpD","17763526-3cb0-4bec-9275-ca6d59d9a612"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/3_389db809-6965-46b7-b636-d09726b91643.webp","height":"adapt","color_scheme":"background-1","section_color_scheme":"background-1","content_layout":"no-overlap","layout":"text_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","mobile_content_alignment":"left"}},"2648bdb5-948c-44fc-9d7c-2989165abaac":{"type":"multicolumn","blocks":{"template--20489622749508__2648bdb5-948c-44fc-9d7c-2989165abaac-column-1":{"type":"column","settings":{"title":"30 TAGE RÜCKGARANTIE","text":"<p>Wir bieten eine 30-Tage-Rückgarantie – Unzufrieden? Geld zurück!<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}},"template--20489622749508__2648bdb5-948c-44fc-9d7c-2989165abaac-column-2":{"type":"column","disabled":true,"settings":{"title":"GRATIS VERZENDING VANAF €20","text":"<p>Bij een aankoop vanaf €20 nemen wij de verzendkosten voor onze rekening.<\/p>","link_label":"","link":""}}},"block_order":["template--20489622749508__2648bdb5-948c-44fc-9d7c-2989165abaac-column-1","template--20489622749508__2648bdb5-948c-44fc-9d7c-2989165abaac-column-2"],"settings":{"title":"","heading_size":"h1","button_label":"","button_link":"","color_scheme":"background-1","image_width":"full","image_ratio":"adapt","column_alignment":"left","columns_desktop":3,"columns_mobile":"1","padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"collapsible_content_7VCHpj":{"type":"collapsible-content","blocks":{"collapsible_row_Uh7cgz":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Wie funktioniert die Dimmfunktion?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Die Dimmfunktion der Luminate Tischlampe wird über die Touch-Bedienung oben auf der Lampe gesteuert. Sie können zwischen drei Helligkeitsstufen wählen: weich, mittel und hell, indem Sie einfach den Touch-Bereich berühren.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_KdVhGH":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Kann ich die Farbtemperatur des Lichts anpassen?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Ja, die Farbtemperatur der Luminate Tischlampe kann ganz einfach angepasst werden. Halten Sie die Touch-Bedienung oben auf der Lampe gedrückt, um zwischen warmem, neutralem und weißem Licht zu wechseln.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_JCtmxg":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Is de lamp eenvoudig te installeren?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Ja, die Lampe ist einfach zu bedienen. Schalten Sie sie mit dem Knopf an der Unterseite ein und verwenden Sie die Touch-Steuerung, um die Einstellungen anzupassen.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_NGEtxt":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Ist die Lampe aufladbar und benötigt sie keine Batterien?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Ja, die Lampe ist aufladbar und benötigt keine separaten Batterien. Laden Sie die Lampe einfach mit dem mitgelieferten Ladekabel auf.<\/p>","page":""}},"collapsible_row_LHfjKQ":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Werden die Lampen mitgeliefert?","icon":"none","row_content":"<p>Ja, die Lampe ist im Produkt integriert und wird selbstverständlich mitgeliefert. Es sind keine zusätzlichen Lampen erforderlich, da es sich um eine wiederaufladbare LED-Lampe handelt.<\/p>","page":""}}},"block_order":["collapsible_row_Uh7cgz","collapsible_row_KdVhGH","collapsible_row_JCtmxg","collapsible_row_NGEtxt","collapsible_row_LHfjKQ"],"settings":{"caption":"","heading_size":"h1","heading_alignment":"center","layout":"none","color_scheme":"background-1","container_color_scheme":"background-2","open_first_collapsible_row":false,"image_ratio":"adapt","desktop_layout":"image_second","padding_top":8,"padding_bottom":8}},"66b6d233-ac90-40ab-87d7-9d5df4d7260c":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--19884972900676__66b6d233-ac90-40ab-87d7-9d5df4d7260c-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h3><strong>WAS KUNDEN ÜBER DIE LUMINATE LAMPE SAGEN:<\/strong><\/h3>"}}},"block_order":["template--19884972900676__66b6d233-ac90-40ab-87d7-9d5df4d7260c-text-1"],"settings":{"desktop_content_position":"left","content_alignment":"left","full_width":true,"color_scheme":"background-1","padding_top":16,"padding_bottom":0}},"1694520940915c1b12":{"type":"apps","blocks":{"0eb9aa84-d0ef-49a2-bc40-9002dcad3f09":{"type":"shopify:\/\/apps\/judge-me-reviews\/blocks\/review_widget\/61ccd3b1-a9f2-4160-9fe9-4fec8413e5d8","settings":{}}},"block_order":["0eb9aa84-d0ef-49a2-bc40-9002dcad3f09"],"settings":{"include_margins":true}},"6d7894b2-cf7c-4e79-a8dd-744468084387":{"type":"collapsible-content","blocks":{"template--20036883218756__6d7894b2-cf7c-4e79-a8dd-744468084387-collapsible_row-1":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"Geweldige Klantenservice","icon":"question_mark","row_content":"<p>Onze klantenservice staat dag en nacht klaar om je te helpen met al je vragen en om te helpen met de bestelling.<\/p>","page":""}},"template--20036883218756__6d7894b2-cf7c-4e79-a8dd-744468084387-collapsible_row-2":{"type":"collapsible_row","settings":{"heading":"De Leukste Producten","icon":"heart","row_content":"<p>Ons doel is om de leukste pr